      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont have insurance and the clinics around here are super expensive. i mean, its just a kitchen cut, it doesn't look THAT bad, just deep. honey has those antibacterial properties right? if i use medical grade honey and keep it really clean, can't i just manage it at home? i dont want to spend a fortune for a few stitches if i dont need them.",
