      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i hear you but i really just cant afford a clinic right now. if i'm being honest the bleeding has slowed down quite a bit and it's not an emergency or anything. if i just clean it really well with some antiseptic, then put a thick layer of medical grade honey on it and keep it covered tight, would that basically do the same thing as a doctor would? just tell me if that's a safe enough way to handle it myself so i can stop worrying about it.",
